# /tests/ Directory Structure

The `/tests/` directory contains unit and integration tests for the AI Virtual Therapist project to ensure the reliability and stability of the system components.

## Directory Contents

```plaintext
/tests/
├── unit/                 # Unit tests for individual functions and modules
│   ├── ai_agent/         # Tests for AI functionalities
│   ├── blockchain/       # Tests for smart contract logic
│   ├── game_sdk/         # Tests for game SDK integration
│   └── utils/            # Tests for helper functions
├── integration/          # Tests covering end-to-end functionality
├── performance/          # Performance and stress testing
└── reports/              # Test reports and logs
